          <span class="italic">The Security Council</span>,</p>
      </formula>
      <container name="Reaffirming" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Reaffirming</span> all its resolutions on Cyprus, in particular resolution 1250 (1999) of 29 June 1999 aimed at achieving agreement on a comprehensive Cyprus settlement,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Reiterating" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Reiterating</span> its strong interest in achieving an overall political settlement on Cyprus which takes full consideration of relevant Security Council resolutions and treaties,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Welcoming" eId="container_4">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Welcoming</span> the report of the Secretary-General of 1 April 2003 (S/2003/398) on his mission of good offices in Cyprus,</p>
